Third-party engines and skills — whether open-source or proprietary /
closed-source — may plug into PYSHA through Python entry-point groups
(pysha.engines.stt, pysha.engines.tts, pysha.engines.llm, pysha.skills).
Such plugins remain the property of their authors and may be distributed
under any license the author chooses.  Linking a proprietary plugin to
